# Layout Test - Checklist with Results

## Urban Routes Homepage

| Nº  | Description of Review                                                                                     | Chrome (800x600) | Firefox (1920x1080) | Bug Report Link                                                 |
|-----|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------|---------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| 1   | When accessing Urban.Routes, the "From" and "To" fields are empty.                                        | Approved         | Approved            |                                                                |
| 2   | The name "PLATFORM" is displayed next to the Urban.Routes website logo.                                    | Rejected         | Rejected            | [KAN-25](https://gleniofilhoo.atlassian.net/browse/KAN-25)     |
| 3   | The Urban.Routes website logo is displayed when accessing the site.                                       | Approved         | Approved            |                                                                |
| 4   | Two circles (red and blue) are displayed next to the "From" and "To" fields, indicating the addresses.     | Approved         | Approved            |                                                                |
| 5   | When typing invalid addresses, the fields turn red, indicating that a valid address is required.          | Approved         | Approved            |                                                                |

